kms_key.description: A reference to a Cloud KMS CryptoKey that can be used for CMEK in the requested product/project/location, for example 'projects/1/locations/us-east1/keyRings/foo/cryptoKeys/bar-ffffff'

location.description: The location for the KeyHandle. A full list of valid locations can be found by running 'gcloud kms locations list'.

name.description: The resource name for the KeyHandle.

resource_type_selector.description: Selector of the resource type where we want to protect resources. For example, 'storage.googleapis.com/Bucket'.
